{"tid":1696291,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲逾百少女遭警方密室脫衣搜身　最小僅12歲","createTime":"2019-11-06T05:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T10:13:55.000Z","uid":10540,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a7536758af447716836f701c4b892d017670b4e6","tid":1696291,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:51:20.000Z","msg":"就去年警方在Splendour草地音樂節涉嫌向一名16歲少女非法脫衣搜身，新州警方監管機構進行調查，發現自2016年起，共有122名18歲以下少女遭警方脫衣搜身。<br />\n<br />\n據Redfern法律中心的數據顯示<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">，自2016年以來新州警方共對女性進行3919次脫衣搜身，其中近一半年僅25歲或以下。而令人最震驚的是，警方曾要求兩名12歲及八名13歲少女脫衣搜身</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n該中心的Samantha Lee批評，新州搜身法例無法保障兒童權益。她表示，「有些女童年僅12或13歲，剛小學畢業，突然被警方帶到密室要求脫衣&hellip;&hellip;不難想像她們感到害怕和驚慌，而且大多數對自身法律權利一無所知」。<br />\n<br />\n上月，執法行為委員會就該緝毒拘捕行動舉行公開聽證會。會上聞悉，該名少女被迫脫光衣服蹲在一名警員面前，然後被警員「從下而上」看著她，令她「嚇至不停哭泣」。而且新州警方沒有通知其父母或監護人陪同進行搜身，涉嫌違反警權。<br />\n<br />\n然而，新州警務廳長艾略特(David Elliott)回應有關數字時表示，「即使是兒童，如果警方懷疑他犯罪，我仍希望警員進行脫衣搜身」。<br />\n<br />\n他續稱，「自擔任少年司法廳長以來，我們曾接獲有10歲兒童參與恐怖活動」。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，該委員會亦正調查警員在脫衣搜查中強迫蹲下是否合法。據悉這是新州警方的普遍做法。今年9月警方首次公佈新個人搜身指引，容許警員指示蹲下、抬起罩丸或胸部、或撥開臀部。<br />\n<br />\n在新州，警方容許在緊急或嚴峻情況下進行即場脫衣搜身。在少數情況下，除非關乎安危或避免毀証，才必須由一名家長或監護人陪同下進行搜身。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/nsw-police-strip-searched-more-than-100-girls-including-12-year-olds?fbclid=IwAR1B6D-Z-3-YXpos8VQqMk9RYQXR2os44Ish_uQAOOUiQNztiinVQRzAkIk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Flanguage%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Fnsw-police-strip-searched-more-than-100-girls-including-12-year-olds%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1B6D-Z-3-YXpos8VQqMk9RYQXR2os44Ish_uQAOOUiQNztiinVQRzAkIk&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX%2BDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=b0a3c4e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/nsw-police-strip-searched-more-than-100-girls-including-12-year-olds?fbclid=IwAR1B6D-Z-3-YXpos8VQqMk9RYQXR2os44Ish_uQAOOUiQNztiinVQRzAkIk</a>"},{"pid":"8a03c58d6b0c4a9cda353203ab500ddda70764a3","tid":1696291,"uid":126329,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:52:22.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗拎埋支私家棍出黎探穴睇下有沒違禁品呀屌"},{"pid":"7e154fbec2774dabd47a7a725f59d27e3bfb53c8","tid":1696291,"uid":302976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:53:39.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf76fe5110b1764c74a123e6ea69ebdeaffd5a77","tid":1696291,"uid":36915,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:54:21.000Z","msg":"天下黑狗甘黑"},{"pid":"2147d90b3f18d21a06f30c00445f4713ff6cc33c","tid":1696291,"uid":217641,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:57:17.000Z","msg":"Absolute power corrupts absolutely."},{"pid":"a6b82af797a7032ecc90ece4c086078029ba0ac6","tid":1696291,"uid":22590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:57:43.000Z","msg":"shop lyfter咩"},{"pid":"02b9a863b8d170f72b6bdb15f339e74197969edb","tid":1696291,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:58:06.000Z","msg":"中共班武警滲入左澳洲警察？"},{"pid":"6f527d609abdc38d4bbf081a61e0253dd10cc177","tid":1696291,"uid":129848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:59:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05d34daea17d3c9d846772d87f4d677d56f4127","tid":1696291,"uid":132128,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:59:35.000Z","msg":"處女膜都check埋"},{"pid":"ffe91937c46b924510b210bd1d721de9db0ac658","tid":1696291,"uid":222970,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T0